snippet.title: [100%] The Amazing Spider-Man: Webslinger 2006 (Java) - Walkthrough
snippet.description:
That's a weird, but very catchy game if you know how to play it. There was no video about this game (except two spider-man java games reviews) on YouTube, so I decided to complete all levels in one video to show you the good things about this game.

0:00 - Menu
1:20 - Level 1
3:49 - Level 2
6:34 - Level 3
9:43 - Level 4
13:02 - Level 5
16:42 - Level 6
20:57 - Level 7
25:52 - Level 8
32:27 - Survival mode
Survival is an endless version of each level, so I didn't want to show them all...

That's all about this game and as you can see - Green Goblin is defeatable...

----------------------------------
Java playlist:
https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLNGa1kVSWDk1SigG7rMHRQcYLnmtfOVtS
Played on PC using KEmulator.
